OL,3,CPSNI and Met probe school 'hoax' email
OL,5,FThe PSNI is working with the
OL,6,FMetropolitan Police to investigate a
OL,7,Fpossible link between threatening
OL,8,Femails sent to schools in Northern
OL,9,FIreland, and similar incidents in
OL,10,FLondon earlier this month.
OL,12,FNine schools were targeted in
OL,13,FStrabane, Enniskillen and Ballycastle,
OL,14,Fwith six forced to close on Monday.
OL,16,FWhile the threats have been declared a
OL,17,Fhoax, it was a day of disruption for
OL,18,Fthousands of pupils, parents and
OL,19,Fteachers.
