OL,3,CPSNI and Met probe school 'hoax' email
OL,5,FPolice said officers were immediately
OL,6,Fdeployed to each school to engage with
OL,7,Fstaff.
OL,9,FA PSNI statement said: "Checks have
OL,10,Fnot, at this time, resulted in
OL,11,Fanything untoward at any of the
OL,12,Fschools. Based on enquiries and
OL,13,Finformation to date, police are
OL,14,Ftreating this as a hoax. Enquiries are
OL,15,Fcontinuing.
OL,17,F"Three schools in Enniskillen who
OL,18,Freceived the email stayed open while
OL,19,Fthe schools in Ballycastle and three
OL,20,Fin Strabane closed."
