OL,3,CPSNI and Met probe school 'hoax' email
OL,5,FChief Superintendent Gillian Kearney
OL,6,Fadded: "We take incidents of this
OL,7,Fnature very seriously and we
OL,8,Funderstand the concern in the
OL,9,Fcommunity, not to mention the
OL,10,Fdisruption it has caused in each of
OL,11,Fthe school communities and for
OL,12,Fstudents and parents.
OL,14,F"Thank you to each of the schools for
OL,15,Ftheir assistance with our enquiries to
OL,16,Fdate.
OL,18,F"Our enquiries are ongoing and we will
OL,19,Fcontinue to liaise with each of the
OL,20,Fschools impacted to provide
OL,21,Freassurance.
