OL,5,F"We urge everyone, in the meantime, to
OL,6,Fbe vigilant and report anything
OL,7,Fsuspicious to police immediately by
OL,8,Fcalling 101, or 999 in an emergency."
OL,10,FPolice said it the disruption was due
OL,11,Fto an email sent to schools and they
OL,12,Fwere working with the Metropolitan
OL,13,FPolice in London. The Education
OL,14,FAuthority referred press queries to
OL,15,Fthe PSNI.
OL,17,FNorth Antrim MP Jim Allister said:
OL,18,F"Appalling to see NI schools closed
OL,19,Fbecause of a security threat,
OL,20,Fincluding Cross & Passion College in
OL,21,FBallycastle in North Antrim.
