OL,5,F"I trust the police get on top of this
OL,6,Fsituation quickly and that concerns of
OL,7,Fparents, staff and pupils can be
OL,8,Fallayed."
OL,10,FAlliance MLA Sian Mulholland said
OL,11,F"security concerns" had closed Cross
OL,12,Fand Passion College, St Patrick's & St
OL,13,FBrigid's Primary School, Ballycastle
OL,14,FIntegrated P.S & Nursery Unit and
OL,15,FGaelscoil an Chaistil in Ballycastle
OL,16,Fwith parents asked to collect their
OL,17,Fchildren.
OL,19,F"This is so concerning, and I'm
OL,20,Fthinking of the impact on the
OL,21,Fschoolchildren at each school.
