OL,6,Fto the schools and for the support
OL,7,Fnetworks of grandparents and family
OL,8,Fmembers etc for stepping in (personal
OL,9,Fthanks to my mother-in-law!) and thank
OL,10,Fyou to the teachers in the schools for
OL,11,Fcontrolling the situation and keeping
OL,12,Four children safe."
OL,14,FDUP MLA for Fermanagh and South
OL,15,FTyrone, Deborah Erskine, said:
OL,16,F"Threats issued against what we
OL,17,Fbelieve to be nine schools across
