OL,3,CPSNI and Met probe school 'hoax' email
OL,5,F"Whilst we await more detail as to
OL,6,Ftheir credibility, such threats are
OL,7,Funacceptable and have no place in our
OL,8,Fsociety. Targeting schools - places of
OL,9,Flearning, personal growth, and
OL,10,Ffriendship for young people - is
OL,11,Fparticularly reprehensible.
OL,13,F"I commend the leadership of the
OL,14,Faffected schools for their swift and
OL,15,Fresponsible response in prioritising
OL,16,Fthe safety and well-being of their
OL,17,Fpupils and staff. Their
OL,18,Fprofessionalism and dedication in the
OL,19,Fface of this situation is testament to
OL,20,Ftheir commitment to their school
OL,21,Fcommunity.
