OL,5,F"My thoughts are with all the pupils,
OL,6,Fparents, and staff impacted by this
OL,7,Fincident and subsequent school
OL,8,Fclosures. No child should have their
OL,9,Feducation disrupted in this manner,
OL,10,Fand no family should have to endure
OL,11,Fthe fear and uncertainty caused by
OL,12,Fsuch reckless actions.
OL,14,F"The PSNI must act swiftly to identify
OL,15,Fthe culprit behind this."
OL,17,FThree schools in the Strabane area
OL,18,Fclosed including Strabane Academy,
OL,19,FStrabane Primary and Holy Cross
OL,20,FCollege.
