OL,3,CPSNI and Met probe school 'hoax' email
OL,5,FIn a statement, the Education
OL,6,FAuthority said: "We have been working
OL,7,Fclosely with PSNI who have confirmed
OL,8,Fthat the threatening email sent to
OL,9,Fnine schools in Northern Ireland today
OL,10,Fis being treated as a hoax.
OL,12,F"PSNI immediately attended each school
OL,13,Fto engage with staff, and checks have
OL,14,Fnot resulted in anything untoward
OL,15,Fbeing identified at any of the
OL,16,Fschools. Police enquiries are
OL,17,Fcontinuing, and they will continue to
OL,18,Fliaise with each of the impacted
OL,19,Fschools. We are very grateful to PSNI
OL,20,Ffor their rapid response to this issue.
